headline: Edwards Lifesciences (EW) Earnings Transcript
summary: Bernard Zovighian: Thank you, Mark and welcome everyone.  This strong Q3 results represent another quarter of double-digit sales growth.  Sales in the quarter grew 12.6% to $1.55 billion driven by our comprehensive portfolio across multiple therapeutic areas, aortic, pulmonic, mitral and tricuspid as well and -- as well as an established presence in countries around the world.
